  <brief_title>Equine-assisted Intervention on Psychosocial Adjustment in Patients With Psychiatric Disorders</brief_title>
  <acronym>PEGASE</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Efficacy of an Equine-assisted Intervention on the Psychosocial Adjustment of Adult Patients Hospitalized and Monitored in Psychiatry: a Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
