  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the efficacy of a brief equine-assisted intervention&#xD;
      on the social adjustment, assertiveness, self-esteem and coping strategies in adult patients&#xD;
      with psychosocial dysfunction, hospitalized and followed in psychiatry, as compared to&#xD;
      standard care.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
